  "title": "English Language Tutor (Primary Level & Secondary) [Tanjong Pagar | 6 days | up to $5000] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>English Language Teacher (Primary Level & Secondary)</strong></h3><p><strong>Working Days: 5/6 working days (include Saturday & Sunday)</strong></p><p><strong>Working Timing: 9am to 8pm </strong></p><p><strong>Basic Salary: $3500 to $5000 (Depends work experience)</strong></p><p><strong>Address: Tanjong Pagar</strong></p><p><u><strong>Requirement </strong></u></p><ul><li><p><strong>Bachelor’s degree</strong> and <strong>at least 3 years</strong> of teaching experience.</p></li><li>Willingness to work during evenings, weekends, public holidays and peak periods</li></ul><p><u>Responsibilities:</u></p><ul><li>Plan and deliver English language composition writing and English language lessons in accordance with the Company's guidelines and framework to achieve desired learning outcomes.</li><li>Adapt teaching methodologies to meet individual student needs.</li><li>Engage and motivate students through interactive and dynamic lessons.</li><li>Demonstrate initiative and proactive behavior in the classroom.</li><li>Ensure punctuality and strong time management skills.</li><li>Communicate effectively and demonstrate problem-solving skills.</li><li>Develop and customize lesson plans to align with students’ requirements.</li><li>Provide written feedback on student progress.</li><li>Create and improve curriculum materials as needed.</li><li>Identify and address learning obstacles faced by students.</li><li>Supervise students during peak hours and maintain classroom discipline.</li><li>Perform other ad hoc tasks as assigned.</li></ul><p><br />Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
